bio.openEndedText: Hi!! Welcome to my newest  entrepreneurial idea, Turo Rentals! Thanks for choosing us and please send us a note with any questions anytime!

Exceptional customer service is THE top priority. 
See other cars in the fleet at www.CarsByJ.com

Locally owned and operated car rental company serving the city of Cleveland, Ohio. Our goal is to provide reliable and affordable transportation options for individuals and families in the area.

Why rent from me?
3000+ trips, with great reviews 
One of Turo's "All-Star" Hosts (Only 5-10% of Turo hosts qualify for this distinction)
Also have been given the distinction of “Power Host”
Instant booking (no need to wait for approval) for Home Location 
Cars available for pick-up/drop off 9am-9pm through contactless check-in
Same day bookings available
I don’t have any papers to sign.
You have confidence in knowing if you book it; it will be available. I have not canceled any trips for any reasons ever. 
Flexibility: If you need to drop the car off early it's no problem. Request the change in Turo. If you need it another few hours or days it's no problem as long as there are no other trips booked after yours. Turo will allow you to request a change as long as there are no other trips and I have approved all changes requested. 

Thank you for taking the time to read my profile,
Rich A

bio.employment: Founder of Your Car Buying Advocate
bio.openEndedText:
We are Mike & Corrie Rumple, owners of Your Car Buying Advocate, a car buying concierge service, created to find, locate and negotiate car deals for consumers who have said see-ya-never to the ever-so-common anxiety, stress and time wasting process of buying a car the traditional dealership way. 

We advocate for 🚙 buyers across all 50 states and we’re building a network of Advocates in 2022 to help more and more people. 🎉

💡Mike was a former car salesman until he turned consumer advocate in 2017.

You can read our story here:

www.youcarbuyingadvocate.com/confessions-of-a-former-car-salesman

About our fam…
👨🏼‍💼🙎🏼‍♀️🐵🙈🙉 We have three kids, gagillions of legos buried deep in our carpet and mysterious writings that appear on our walls from time to time. 🖍👦🏼(5) 👦🏼 (4) 👧🏼 (2) 🤔

We have a wild and crazy life but enjoy the excitement and challenges of being married and business partners (yikes!) while balancing raising kids. 🤪

My favorite car I have owned was the Lincoln MKZ. I loved how smooth the ride was. When I don’t need an SUV to tote around kids and friends and baseball gear and a million groceries, I think I’ll return to my first love. 💕 Until then, there’s Turo. -Corrie

We hope you enjoy our vehicle and we look forward to providing 
clean, convenient, safe and comfortable transportation.

Thanks For Renting With,
The Rumple’s

Hi, my name is Vitaliy I’m from Ukraine and I’ve been running a customer service oriented business for 15 years.  With this flawless track record I am now hosting your car ride.  Absolutely love customer satisfaction as it’s the greatest reward of being in business.

We aim to cater to the desires of discerning individuals who seek not just transportation,  but a statement of their refined taste and style.
